 Here is how to renew your car licence in five easy steps To get started is very easy. There are three options to get started: Submit your car registration number. You will need your ID book to complete your renewal.  Get a quote and pay via the PayFast system which is secure, fast and simple. ALSO READ: Fire raging near White River Check the status of your renewal by sending “status” to the ChatBack WhatsApp number and they will inform you on the status of your renewal. And that is it. Simple, easy and affordable.  See the step-by-step instructions and the QR code from ChatBack here